      "x": 670,
      "y": 140,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 100,
      "text": "Exact Jaccard\n\n|A ∩ B| = 4\n|A ∪ B| = 7\n\nJ = 4/7 = 0.571",
      "originalText": "Exact Jaccard\n\n|A ∩ B| = 4\n|A ∪ B| = 7\n\nJ = 4/7 = 0.571",
